h thy blood the land wherein thou swimmest, even to the mountains; and the rivers shall be full of thee.","year":-587},{"id":"recGk8ACZjWA1T5Ed","ref":"Ezek.32.7","text":"And when I shall put thee out, I will cover the heaven, and make the stars thereof dark; I will cover the sun with a cloud, and the moon shall not give her light.","year":-587},{"id":"recM8bOEaCF6saGN6","ref":"Ezek.32.8","text":"All the bright lights of heaven will I make dark over thee, and set darkness upon thy land, saith the Lord GOD.","year":-587}]}
